27static struct screen *window_buffer_init(struct window_pane *,
28 struct cmd_find_state *, struct args *);
29static void window_buffer_free(struct window_pane *);
30static void window_buffer_resize(struct window_pane *, u_int,
31 u_int);
32static void window_buffer_key(struct window_pane *,
33 struct client *, struct session *, key_code,
34 struct mouse_event *);

36#define WINDOW_BUFFER_DEFAULT_COMMAND "paste-buffer -b '%%'"
37
38#define WINDOW_BUFFER_DEFAULT_FORMAT \
39 "#{buffer_size} bytes (#{t:buffer_created})"
40
41const struct window_mode window_buffer_mode = {
42 .name = "buffer-mode",
43
44 .init = window_buffer_init,
45 .free = window_buffer_free,
46 .resize = window_buffer_resize,
47 .key = window_buffer_key,
48};
49
50enum window_buffer_sort_type {
51 WINDOW_BUFFER_BY_TIME,
52 WINDOW_BUFFER_BY_NAME,
53 WINDOW_BUFFER_BY_SIZE,
54};
55static const char *window_buffer_sort_list[] = {
56 "time",
57 "name",
58 "size"
59};
60
61struct window_buffer_itemdata {
62 const char *name;
63 u_int order;
64 size_t size;
65};
66
67struct window_buffer_modedata {
68 struct mode_tree_data *data;
69 char *command;
70 char *format;
71
72 struct window_buffer_itemdata **item_list;
73 u_int item_size;
74};
75
76static struct window_buffer_itemdata *
77window_buffer_add_item(struct window_buffer_modedata *data)
78{
79 struct window_buffer_itemdata *item;
80
81 data->item_list = xreallocarray(data->item_list, data->item_size + 1,
82 sizeof *data->item_list);
83 item = data->item_list[data->item_size++] = xcalloc(1, sizeof *item);
84 return (item);
85}
86
87static void
88window_buffer_free_item(struct window_buffer_itemdata *item)
89{
90 free(__UNCONST(item->name));
91 free(item);
92}
93
94static int
95window_buffer_cmp_name(const void *a0, const void *b0)
96{
97 const struct window_buffer_itemdata *const *a = a0;
98 const struct window_buffer_itemdata *const *b = b0;
99
100 return (strcmp((*a)->name, (*b)->name));
101}
102
103static int
104window_buffer_cmp_time(const void *a0, const void *b0)
105{
106 const struct window_buffer_itemdata *const *a = a0;
107 const struct window_buffer_itemdata *const *b = b0;
108
109 if ((*a)->order > (*b)->order)
110 return (-1);
111 if ((*a)->order < (*b)->order)
112 return (1);
113 return (strcmp((*a)->name, (*b)->name));
114}
115
116static int
117window_buffer_cmp_size(const void *a0, const void *b0)
118{
119 const struct window_buffer_itemdata *const *a = a0;
120 const struct window_buffer_itemdata *const *b = b0;
121
122 if ((*a)->size > (*b)->size)
123 return (-1);
124 if ((*a)->size < (*b)->size)
125 return (1);
126 return (strcmp((*a)->name, (*b)->name));
127}
128
129static void
130window_buffer_build(void *modedata, u_int sort_type, __unused uint64_t *tag,
131 const char *filter)
132{
133 struct window_buffer_modedata *data = modedata;
134 struct window_buffer_itemdata *item;
135 u_int i;
136 struct paste_buffer *pb;
137 char *text, *cp;
138 struct format_tree *ft;
139
140 for (i = 0; i < data->item_size; i++)
141 window_buffer_free_item(data->item_list[i]);
142 free(data->item_list);
143 data->item_list = NULL;
144 data->item_size = 0;
145
146 pb = NULL;
147 while ((pb = paste_walk(pb)) != NULL) {
148 item = window_buffer_add_item(data);
149 item->name = xstrdup(paste_buffer_name(pb));
150 paste_buffer_data(pb, &item->size);
151 item->order = paste_buffer_order(pb);
152 }
153
154 switch (sort_type) {
155 case WINDOW_BUFFER_BY_NAME:
156 qsort(data->item_list, data->item_size, sizeof *data->item_list,
157 window_buffer_cmp_name);
158 break;
159 case WINDOW_BUFFER_BY_TIME:
160 qsort(data->item_list, data->item_size, sizeof *data->item_list,
161 window_buffer_cmp_time);
162 break;
163 case WINDOW_BUFFER_BY_SIZE:
164 qsort(data->item_list, data->item_size, sizeof *data->item_list,
165 window_buffer_cmp_size);
166 break;
167 }
168
169 for (i = 0; i < data->item_size; i++) {
170 item = data->item_list[i];
171
172 pb = paste_get_name(item->name);
173 if (pb == NULL)
174 continue;
175 ft = format_create(NULL, NULL, FORMAT_NONE, 0);
176 format_defaults_paste_buffer(ft, pb);
177
178 if (filter != NULL) {
179 cp = format_expand(ft, filter);
180 if (!format_true(cp)) {
181 free(cp);
182 format_free(ft);
183 continue;
184 }
185 free(cp);
186 }
187
188 text = format_expand(ft, data->format);
189 mode_tree_add(data->data, NULL, item, item->order, item->name,
190 text, -1);
191 free(text);
192
193 format_free(ft);
194 }
195
196}
197
198static void
199window_buffer_draw(__unused void *modedata, void *itemdata,
200 struct screen_write_ctx *ctx, u_int sx, u_int sy)
201{
202 struct window_buffer_itemdata *item = itemdata;
203 struct paste_buffer *pb;
204 char line[1024];
205 const char *pdata, *end, *cp;
206 size_t psize, at;
207 u_int i, cx = ctx->s->cx, cy = ctx->s->cy;
208
209 pb = paste_get_name(item->name);
210 if (pb == NULL)
211 return;
212
213 pdata = end = paste_buffer_data(pb, &psize);
214 for (i = 0; i < sy; i++) {
215 at = 0;
216 while (end != pdata + psize && *end != '\n') {
217 if ((sizeof line) - at > 5) {
218 cp = vis(line + at, *end, VIS_TAB|VIS_OCTAL, 0);
219 at = cp - line;
220 }
221 end++;
222 }
223 if (at > sx)
224 at = sx;
225 line[at] = '\0';
226
227 if (*line != '\0') {
228 screen_write_cursormove(ctx, cx, cy + i);
229 screen_write_puts(ctx, &grid_default_cell, "%s", line);
230 }
231
232 if (end == pdata + psize)
233 break;
234 end++;
235 }
236}
237
238static int
239window_buffer_search(__unused void *modedata, void *itemdata, const char *ss)
240{
241 struct window_buffer_itemdata *item = itemdata;
242 struct paste_buffer *pb;
243 const char *bufdata;
244 size_t bufsize;
245
246 if ((pb = paste_get_name(item->name)) == NULL)
247 return (0);
248 if (strstr(item->name, ss) != NULL)
249 return (1);
250 bufdata = paste_buffer_data(pb, &bufsize);
251 return (memmem(bufdata, bufsize, ss, strlen(ss)) != NULL);
252}
253
254static struct screen *
255window_buffer_init(struct window_pane *wp, __unused struct cmd_find_state *fs,
256 struct args *args)
257{
258 struct window_buffer_modedata *data;
259 struct screen *s;
260
261 wp->modedata = data = xcalloc(1, sizeof *data);
262
263 if (args == NULL || !args_has(args, 'F'))
264 data->format = xstrdup(WINDOW_BUFFER_DEFAULT_FORMAT);
265 else
266 data->format = xstrdup(args_get(args, 'F'));
267 if (args == NULL || args->argc == 0)
268 data->command = xstrdup(WINDOW_BUFFER_DEFAULT_COMMAND);
269 else
270 data->command = xstrdup(args->argv[0]);
271
272 data->data = mode_tree_start(wp, args, window_buffer_build,
273 window_buffer_draw, window_buffer_search, data,
274 window_buffer_sort_list, nitems(window_buffer_sort_list), &s);
275 mode_tree_zoom(data->data, args);
276
277 mode_tree_build(data->data);
278 mode_tree_draw(data->data);
279
280 return (s);
281}
282
283static void
284window_buffer_free(struct window_pane *wp)
285{
286 struct window_buffer_modedata *data = wp->modedata;
287 u_int i;
288
289 if (data == NULL)
290 return;
291
292 mode_tree_free(data->data);
293
294 for (i = 0; i < data->item_size; i++)
295 window_buffer_free_item(data->item_list[i]);
296 free(data->item_list);
297
298 free(data->format);
299 free(data->command);
300
301 free(data);
302}
303
304static void
305window_buffer_resize(struct window_pane *wp, u_int sx, u_int sy)
306{
307 struct window_buffer_modedata *data = wp->modedata;
308
309 mode_tree_resize(data->data, sx, sy);
310}
311
312static void
313window_buffer_do_delete(void* modedata, void *itemdata,
314 __unused struct client *c, __unused key_code key)
315{
316 struct window_buffer_modedata *data = modedata;
317 struct window_buffer_itemdata *item = itemdata;
318 struct paste_buffer *pb;
319
320 if (item == mode_tree_get_current(data->data))
321 mode_tree_down(data->data, 0);
322 if ((pb = paste_get_name(item->name)) != NULL)
323 paste_free(pb);
324}
325
326static void
327window_buffer_do_paste(void* modedata, void *itemdata, struct client *c,
328 __unused key_code key)
329{
330 struct window_buffer_modedata *data = modedata;
331 struct window_buffer_itemdata *item = itemdata;
332 struct paste_buffer *pb;
333
334 if ((pb = paste_get_name(item->name)) != NULL)
335 mode_tree_run_command(c, NULL, data->command, item->name);
336}
337
338static void
339window_buffer_key(struct window_pane *wp, struct client *c,
340 __unused struct session *s, key_code key, struct mouse_event *m)
341{
342 struct window_buffer_modedata *data = wp->modedata;
343 struct mode_tree_data *mtd = data->data;
344 struct window_buffer_itemdata *item;
345 int finished;
346
347 finished = mode_tree_key(mtd, c, &key, m, NULL, NULL);
348 switch (key) {
349 case 'd':
350 item = mode_tree_get_current(mtd);
351 window_buffer_do_delete(data, item, c, key);
352 mode_tree_build(mtd);
353 break;
354 case 'D':
355 mode_tree_each_tagged(mtd, window_buffer_do_delete, c, key, 0);
356 mode_tree_build(mtd);
357 break;
358 case 'P':
359 mode_tree_each_tagged(mtd, window_buffer_do_paste, c, key, 0);
360 finished = 1;
361 break;
362 case 'p':
363 case '\r':
364 item = mode_tree_get_current(mtd);
365 window_buffer_do_paste(data, item, c, key);
366 finished = 1;
367 break;
368 }
369 if (finished || paste_get_top(NULL) == NULL)
370 window_pane_reset_mode(wp);
371 else {
372 mode_tree_draw(mtd);
373 wp->flags |= PANE_REDRAW;
374 }
375}
